        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Are Cheng Yao's dreams of becoming a top lawyer about to come true? It seems so, when she is unexpectedly recruited by a leading legal firm. Excited, she moves house so she can be near her new office. She moves in, full of hope, and soon encounters her new roommate, Qian Heng. However, a surprise awaits her on her first day at work.\n\nQian Heng turns out to be her direct superior\n\nat the office, and he proves to be incredibly hard to please! Her training period quickly turns into a baptism of fire, and she starts to feel as though he is trying to chase her out of the company. But Cheng Yao won’t be so easily deterred. She redoubles her efforts, determined to prove she’s got what it takes. Could her zeal send this duo on the path to harmony and even love?",
            "source": "mydramalist",
            "source_link": "https://mydramalist.com/70241-ni-ye-you-jin-tian"
        },
